The 64-year-old showcased his ageless appearance as he got rid of his signature moustache which he sports on the programme and instead went natural with a low cut beard. The Hollywood actor chatted with the hosts of The View on August 6 where he discussed his character in the crime drama. His appearance comes just days before the actor shared devastating news on social media. Kevin explained that he and his wife Kyra Sedgwick, 56, had lost their beloved dog, Lily. In view of his 755,000 followers, the actor penned: "Goodbye sweet Lilly. We miss you already." The on-screen star was inundated with condolence messages following the family loss.